title: Average retail price for ground beef in Canada 2015 to 2019
summary: This grouped bar chart represents Average retail price in CAD on the Y-axis. And, its value throughout 12 Months for 2015, 2016, 2017, 2018, and 2019.
Over the 12 Months, the Average retail price in CAD for both 2015 and Month have grew.
Out of all 5 groups, 2015 had the highest Average retail price in CAD in Month Oct and 2019 had the lowest Average retail price in CAD in Month Dec.
In Month Oct, 2015 had the maximum Average retail price in CAD and it saw the lowest in Month Dec out of all 12 Months.
